{"tid":2254903,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"I大禁止帶豬嘴返學！","createTime":"2020-10-23T07:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T08:41:11.000Z","uid":362865,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac543170614a8bb2bfe4224891de00df1425bddb","tid":2254903,"uid":362865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:20:11.000Z","msg":"為保障學生及員工安全和健康，校方提醒所有人士均<span class=\"red\">不可配戴附有氣閥的口罩或呼吸器</span>進入本學院，因呼氣時飛沫可由氣閥排出而增加其他人受感染的潛在危險。請參閱附件內有關附有氣閥的口罩或呼吸器之款式，以及香港考試及考評局相關指引(節錄)，以作參考。學院秘書處會指示學院物業管理公司在院校入口貼出相關告示並提醒入場人士須配戴口罩進入院校。多謝合作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWith due consideration to the health protection and staff &amp; student&rsquo;s concerns, your attention is drawn that the <span class=\"red\">face masks or respirators with valves are not allowed</span> to use in the Campus as respiratory droplets can be dispersed through the valve thus exposing other people to the risk of possible infections. Please refer to the photo attached on the type of face masks embedded with one-way valve(s) for reference. The same face mask requirements are also specified by the Hong Kong Examinations and Assessment Authority which is extracted and attached for your information.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n廢事自爆Cut左少少野<br />\n想睇全文？ TG me hugo1991"},{"pid":"e01644b666ff5ee3be08e2fc1bf043efa84f2ac2","tid":2254903,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"ive d港豬專捉人唔戴罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeac8b0dc9a417964cbcbb90b00ae7c5c93ba684","tid":2254903,"uid":125017,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:24:32.000Z","msg":"戴透明口罩咪無氣閥"},{"pid":"ca7b81bcea79b7abf241456f47ddd4b53ff2df5a","tid":2254903,"uid":32380,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"其實make sen